[[Some argue|Widely]] regarded as a [[pretty cool guy|God among men]] and legend to [[13 year old boy|teenage]] [[fanbois]] everywhere, '''Bruce Campbell's''' [[sarcasm|flawless intonation]], [[Melodramatic|facial expressions]], and sheer [[awesome]]ness have dazzled millions for [[at least 100|many]] years. Best known for his role in the ''[[zombie|Evil Dead]]'' movies and a common topic on [[TV|/tv/]], he's an all-too-common [[ADD|segway]] in [[zombie apocalypse]] threads amongst the [[elitist]] [[anal]]-retentive  uber-[[nerds]] on [[/b/]].  

Bruce Campbell is often portrayed fighting [[zombie]]s and shouting things like [[Duke Nukem 3D|"Hail to the King"]] or [[cunnilingus|"Give me some sugar, baby,"]] and is the author of numerous [[lulz]]y books such as ''[[DO IT FAGGOT|Make Love!]]: [[Stick it in her pooper|The Bruce Campbell Way]]'' and ''[[Unbirthing|If Chins Could Kill]]''. A [[Buttsecks|close friend]] of [[Spiderman|Sam Raimi]], he can still be found in the odd [[crap|b-movie]], [[TV]] spot or [[video game]] here and there, but doesn't have to do shit anymore due to the level of [[epic win]] that he's already [[final boss|achieved]]. For examples, see ''[[Burn]] Notice'' or ''[[fail|The Replacements]]''.

